Dear all,
You could download Kodi Player and Play

Open Terminal.
Run below code
sudo apt-get install kodi
click yes.

Let it completed the setup
or
You can check out the Kodi wiki site
https://kodi.wiki/view/Add-on:PVR_IPTV_Simple_Client

Next step before you run the application.
Please follow the setup first

At the terminal
type
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install kodi-pvr-iptvsimple (only work for the list inside this repo that ive provided)

below is the guide and all source of iptv addon list
https://kodi.wiki/view/Ubuntu_PVR_add-ons
